But this doesn't exscuse her and her husband. Anyway, school starts next week, so I for one will have to finish any big quests (EPIC!) or up some needed faction or Tskills before then..that way I can actually devote some RL time to RL issues.<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Though I would never blame EQ for something like this the danger in compulsive game playing is when you begin to ascribe real importance to the &quot;accomplishments&quot; of the game.<br>
<br>
The best way to safely enjoy a game can be to not play it in a goal oriented fashion.  Don't worry if you don't level, fail a quest or blow a tradeskill combine.  If you find yourself getting too goal driven reroll and start from scratch.<br>
<br>
